# Unit Testing Conventions

When adding unit tests or a new test target:
- Add the target to the `Biker` scheme's Test action.
- Use [Swift Testing](https://developer.apple.com/documentation/testing): `import Testing`, `@Test`, `#expect`.
- Do not use XCTest for new tests.
